			<div class="skill-category">
				<h4>Cloud Security</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>Azure, AWS, GCP environments</li>
					<li>Cloud migration security</li>
					<li>Identity and access management</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			
			<div class="skill-category">
				<h4>Security Operations</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>SIEM implementation (Splunk, QRadar, Sentinel)</li>
					<li>Threat hunting and incident response</li>
					<li>Vulnerability management</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			
			<div class="skill-category">
				<h4>Compliance & Governance</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>NIST frameworks</li>
					<li>FedRAMP certification</li>
					<li>Security policy development</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<h3>My Approach</h3>
		<p>
			I believe in building security solutions that enable business, not hinder it. My consultancy focuses on practical, scalable security measures that protect your assets while supporting your operations and growth. Whether you need comprehensive security architecture or targeted improvements to your existing infrastructure, my approach combines technical expertise with clear communication and business alignment.
		</p>
		
		<h3>Why Choose a Veteran-Owned Business?</h3>
		<p>
			When you work with Morris IT Consulting, you're partnering with a business built on military values of discipline, integrity, and excellence. My service-oriented mindset means your security challenges become my mission, and I'm committed to delivering solutions that exceed expectations, on time and with precision.
		</p>
		
